	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been meaning to do something like this as well.  The test programs by Nintendo may be a good spot to look.  A program that where you could enter an address and a value would also be kinda useful.
<br />
<br />Another suggestion is to write values like $A5 so that you can easily detect data lines.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
